headline.main: Turkey Says Warplane, Probably Syrian, Crashed Near Border
headline.print_headline: Turkey Says Warplane, Probably Syrian, Crashed Near Border

lead_paragraph: A warplane probably belonging to the Syrian air force crashed on the Turkish side of the border with Syria on Saturday and the pilots appeared to have bailed out, a local Turkish governor was quoted as saying.
